citations.desc: Access and inspection of records and property; submission of itineraries.
citations.narrative:
A responsible adult was not available to accompany APHIS Officials during the inspection process at 2:50-3:20pm on 22-
JAN-21. A voicemail was left with no return call within 30 minutes, and there was no response to multiple honks of vehicle
horn while waiting in driveway.
End Section
